	<body>
		<h1 class="bg-blue-800 text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl p-3">
			The Universal Draft Lottery Simulator
		</h1>
		<div class="m-3">
			<div class="alert" id="intro">
				<button
					class="float-right ml-2 text-xl leading-none mt-[-4px] mr-[-4px]"
					type="button"
					onclick="
						localStorage.setItem('hideIntro', '1');
						this.parentNode.style.display = 'none';
					"
					title="Hide intro"
				>
					✕
				</button>
				Calculate the odds and simulate an
				<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NBA_draft_lottery">NBA/MLB/NHL-like draft lottery</a>
				with any number of teams and any probabilities you want. You have complete flexibility in
				how the lottery is generated and performed. Use it for your fantasy league, or just for
				playing around.
			</div>
			<div id="app"><div class="mb-3">Loading...</div></div>
		</div>
		{% include "google-analytics.njk" %}    
